----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Log Analytics Agent
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Natural language → Elasticsearch DSL → Plain English answer
Ask questions about your logs in plain English. Get real answers backed by live data.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Architecture
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Every query passes through a 3-stage LLM pipeline. 
Common queries skip the LLM entirely via intent templates. 
All LLM calls use temperature=0 for deterministic output.

